I have a server that I want everyone to [i][b]"::yell"[/b][/i] and you do not have to be a donator to do so.. So I was wondering where would I change this that it would be available for all people to [i][b]"::yell"[/b][/i]?
<blockquote>if(command.startsWith("yell") && command.length() > 5 && muted == false) {
String titles = "";

if (donator >= 0) {
sM("You need to be a donator to use Yell");
} else {

switch (playerRights) {
case 0:
titles = "[DONATOR] ";
break;

case 1:
titles = "[MOD] ";
break;

case 2:
titles = "[ADMIN] ";
break;

case 3:
titles = "[OWNER] ";
break;

case 4:
titles = "[SERVER] ";
break;
}
yell(titles + playerName + ": " + command.substring(5));</blockquote>
